<section class="project py-md-6 py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="mb-5">
            <p class="lead fw-normal">{{ description }}</p>
            <p class="my-3">
                Over the years, my portfolio site has taken many forms—from simple static HTML pages and Wordpress installs to a custom-built PHP and XML blogging platform. With this latest iteration on 11ty, I enjoy the freedom to design and build creative tools, while keeping the end result simple, fast, and deployable anywhere. It’s a blend of fun challenges and practical solutions that make the process as rewarding as the finished site.
            </p>
            {% include "components/projects/button.njk" %}
        </div>
        <div class="project-details grid g-4 g-md-5 mb-4">
            <div class="g-col-12 g-col-md-6 g-col-xl-4">
                <div class="d-flex h-100">
                    <div class="text-stckr me-4">
                        {% include "svg/11ty.njk" %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex-flex-column">
                        <h2 class="h4 lh-base">Why 11ty?</h2>
                        <p class="m-0">I chose Eleventy (11ty) because it’s fast, flexible, and lets me build exactly the kind of site I want—without getting in my way. Its simplicity and power make it perfect for a creative portfolio.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="g-col-12 g-col-md-6 g-col-xl-4">
                <div class="d-flex h-100">
                    <div class="text-stckr me-4">
                        {% include "svg/bootstrap.njk" %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column">
                        <h2 class="h4 lh-base">Why Bootstrap?</h2>
                        <p class="m-0">I use Bootstrap because it gives me a solid, responsive grid and a ton of utility classes—so I can focus on design and content, not reinventing the basics.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="g-col-12 g-col-md-6 g-col-xl-4">
                <div class="d-flex h-100">
                    <div class="text-stckr me-4">
                        {% include "svg/nunjucks.njk" %}
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column">
                        <h2 class="h4 lh-base">Why Nunjucks?</h2>
                        <p class="m-0">Nunjucks lets me write templates that are clean, readable, and reusable. It’s powerful enough for complex layouts, but simple enough to keep everything maintainable.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-5">
            {% set heroImage = projectId | assetImagePath('png', '', tags, 'lg') %}
            <img src="{{ heroImage | url }}" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm h-100"
                alt="{{ imageAlt or (title ~ ' screenshot') }}">
        </div>
        {% include "components/projects/gallery.njk" %}

        {% set showReturnButton = true %}
        {% set returnButton = "/projects" %}
        {% set returnButtonText = "Back to projects" %}
        {% set itemPaginationCollection = collections.projects %}
        {% set itemPaginationInputPath = page.inputPath %}
        {% include "components/pagination/item.njk" %}
    </div>
</section>